OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBali plans tourist         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmotorbike ban over         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmisbehaviour               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Indonesian island of Bali is       
OL,6, planning to ban foreign tourists from  
OL,7, using motorbikes after a spate of cases
OL,8, involving people breaking traffic laws.
OL,10,F"You (should) not roam about the island
OL,11,Fusing motorbikes, without wearing      
OL,12,Fshirts or clothes, no helmet, and even 
OL,13,Fwithout a licence," Governor I Wayan   
OL,14,FKoster said.                           
OL,16,FUnder the proposals tourists would use 
OL,17,Fcars provided by travel agents instead.
OL,19,FThe plan has been divisive as tourism  
OL,20,Fcontinues to recover from Covid losses.
